				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\times $$\end{document} 102%, and a relaxation time of 0.03 s in the NIR region. In addition, the Al2O3 infiltration increased shelf stability since the Al2O3 is an effective encapsulation material that protects materials vulnerable to outside air. Based on the additional Al2O3 layer deposited by the ALD infiltration process, we offer an effective micro patterned quantum dot/metal oxide hybrid phototransistor with enhanced photoreactivity, photorecovery and air stability.
